lead_paragraph: Because of an editing error, an article on Friday about Julie Coin’s upset of top-seeded Ana Ivanovic, the world’s No. 1-ranked player, at the United States Open misstated, in some editions, the rankings for three other women. Serena Williams is third, not fourth; Elena Dementieva is sixth, not fifth; and Dinara Safina is seventh, not sixth. (The article used their tournament seeds, not their world rankings.).
